nodes.text: Landing Zone I-3 was a landing zone on the Selkath Mercantile Plaza in the Imperial Concourse.

A notice to Offworlders from the Order of Shasa at a nearby droid-staffed cantina stated that the number of beverages that could be bought and consumed in one visit was strictly limited. The sign also reminded visitors to always remain mindful of cultural norms, particularly as regards to maintaining a respectful distance and tone with the Selkath hosts.
